{"tid":2179851,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【快閃南法】普羅旺斯尋覓芳草之旅","createTime":"2020-08-29T12:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T19:19:58.000Z","uid":372699,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b445eee387864661e18fcb5a56121530a6374aff","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"Salut! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018年嘅暑假，書生我有幸拎到學校funding去法國一個summer 學下法文同自己科嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，於是戇居居咁就去咗見識巴黎嘅日與夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，估唔到呢個決定對我嘅人生會帶嚟好重大嘅影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gk852sR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGk852sR.jpg&h=61c3721e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺嗰度每日日頭都要上堂，落堂先得幾個鐘同weekend去玩，可想而知成個Trip都幾chur下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，後來又有啲審美疲勞，有啲地方去嗰時都係走馬看花、跑景點就算，睇翻啲相都好似差啲嘢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以一直都想寫篇遊記，整合返喺法國零零碎碎嘅記憶，於是就決定襯肺炎喺屋企寫篇遊記同大家分享，當重新去一次，解下旅遊癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，順便為有機會去法國嘅人提供少少資訊 (雖然去嘅地方唔多，有錯嘅話請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢一個月嘅經歷可以話係百年難得一遇，完全無諗過自己可以喺一個月入面學識用法文生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、喺六月底竟然都快閃睇到南法普羅旺斯嘅薰衣草<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、坐喺鐵塔下面暴曬慶祝法國國慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、第二日仲可以見證法國拎世界盃冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、又坐喺凱旋門下面睇環法單車賽終點站。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個月時間話短唔短、話長唔長。雖然可能只係體驗到好表面嘅生活，但係都想同大家分享下我眼中嘅法國，希望你哋會同我一齊重溫呢段咁難忘嘅旅程啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n今次首先同大家分享下我快閃南法普羅旺斯追薰衣草嘅經歷先，有人想睇巴黎、中歐遊記先再貼啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 由於小弟仲係一個窮鬼書生，得部辣殺手機影相，啲相放大係完全唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，執咗幾張我都放棄，講聲唔好意思先！<br />\n<br />\n行程表：<br />\nDay 1 - Day 4：【普羅旺斯尋覓芳草之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YW5zV3m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYW5zV3m.jpg&h=d045453d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLrO0vb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLrO0vb.jpg&h=73f0e06d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzf8f3D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgzf8f3D.jpg&h=0f51ac15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o13qig8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo13qig8.jpg&h=4adb5975&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zq1GA3R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZq1GA3R.jpg&h=c6d812ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yd0HkvF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYd0HkvF.jpg&h=2f4770d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 5 - Day 36: 【我在巴黎當書生的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />】<br />\n<br />\n基本上巴黎主要嘅景點都去得七七八八<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BWmLigY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBWmLigY.png&h=c93b7347&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nJ住巴黎鐵塔三部曲先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zftYDh2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzftYDh2.jpg&h=504d51c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UhDBpYb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUhDBpYb.jpg&h=a5d1e1c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TJq8f4R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTJq8f4R.jpg&h=79aa7143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 37 - Day 52 【一路向東遊中歐】<br />\n(完咗之後仲有少少時間，一路向東去咗15日Munich、Prague、Budapest、Bratislava同Vienna，如果大家有任何問題都可以問我架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n而家即刻出發！Allons-y！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f900dc1f44c807c2dd7a5326c3d4d9b2a5bea7c6","tid":2179851,"uid":20160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"Support, exchange 真係令人回味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb583f2e9285bad21607da937d2f34431fdf0e42","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f900dc1f44c807c2dd7a5326c3d4d9b2a5bea7c6","tid":2179851,"uid":20160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"Support, exchange 真係令人回味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你果陣去邊呀？<br />\n<br />\n之前有機會去多一個sem<br />\n但係因為一啲原因去唔成<br />\n而家好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5df84196f7e4b75e32fbe16346dbf41b62cf236","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T02:43:43.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\">   <span class=\"large\">  Day 1： 抵達巴黎 法國龜速日常、抗爭生活初體驗 前往南法普羅旺斯<br />\n  </span>    </span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">  是日路線：巴黎 Paris &rarr; 尼姆 Nimes<br />\n<br />\n交通： 里昂車站 Gare de Lyon &rarr; Nimes (TGV)<br />\n </span><br />\n(第一日落機發生咗好多突如其來嘅事，實在太chur太攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以冇乜點影相，之後會多翻啲架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。)<br />\n<br />\n經歷咗十幾個鐘嘅機程後，我哋終於到咗巴黎喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！喺過關嘅時侯已經開始感受到法國人慢條斯理嘅生活節奏。就算見到前面有過百人等緊過關，啲職員都可以慢慢咁對你嘅資料、問你問題、打手指模。最後我哋用咗個幾鐘先出到機場。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我哋去咗嚟緊一個月會住嘅地方擺低個行李箱，再出發去里昂車站搭車去南法嘅尼姆(Nimes)。點知我哋到咗轉車站，先發現我哋撞正法國鐵路罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rh6Z8aV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRh6Z8aV.png&h=78c601eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原本嘅月台冇開、啲列車又喺唔同嘅月台開出、連啲職員都答唔到我哋要去邊。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我哋之後用咗半個鐘周圍行周圍問，誤打誤撞之下上咗架啱嘅車先脱離到個轉車站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真係冇諗到一落地就可以用兩個鐘體驗法國人嘅抗爭生活態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，最後我哋緊係趕唔到車啦，我哋仲要一早book好晒車飛同住宿，如果今日去唔到就真係蝕晒大本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。不幸中之大幸係我哋去到客戶服務中心嘅時候，個staff幫我哋改搭遲6個鐘後嘅火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n改完飛之後，我哋就求其喺附近搵咗間小型嘅藝術館行下（而家已經執咗，名都搵唔返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）。呢間藝術館比我嘅感覺係幾新派，入面有好多唔同嘅藝術裝置，有啲仲可以比你體驗下，所以都幾好玩，好快就渡過咗呢幾個鐘，終於出發去Nimes！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gjBvvrb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgjBvvrb.jpg&h=f50125dc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span class=\"blue\"> P.S.  因為我哋有EU學生證，所以好多博物館、景點都有discount/免費。如果仲係25歲以下/學生，可以考慮請國際學生證isic/青年證iytc架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n  </span><br />\n<br />\n去到嘅時侯已經夜晚八點，好彩歐洲日照長成10點先日落，我哋仲有時間慢慢行去住嘅地方。唔知係咪歐洲地方大，感覺冇喺香港高樓大廈咁大壓逼感，行步路都輕鬆過人。喺南法呢邊終於明白點解法國人個個都優哉悠哉咁，日日對住咁心礦神怡、咁chill嘅環境，係人都會不自覺咁放慢腳步享受啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZT3NxEm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZT3NxEm.jpg&h=b44d186a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不知不覺行到酒店就日落喇，我哋就爭取時間快啲梳洗、休息，迎接呢幾日周圍跳嚟跳去嘅旅程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/464EoLR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F464EoLR.jpg&h=ff21ae06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 1 end"},{"pid":"79131f6dcd0ff7b382e405ae3e1ca4b3de5d04fb","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T04:16:26.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果覺得好睇可以留個正評 / cm交流下架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d23a545296203191f3f6850d9be38759e8bf39","tid":2179851,"uid":312108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:38:00.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係2018去法國summer exchange 睇完你第一句差啲以為我識你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我學校喺南法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔識睇波 但見證住啲法國人攞世界盃真係好好氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016ac9a9ad941a35b5f186e78eb6fa49f12a7ef6","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26d23a545296203191f3f6850d9be38759e8bf39","tid":2179851,"uid":312108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T07:38:00.000Z","msg":"留名支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都係2018去法國summer exchange 睇完你第一句差啲以為我識你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過我學校喺南法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然唔識睇波 但見證住啲法國人攞世界盃真係好好氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T08:22:29.000Z","msg":"多謝絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\