s</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcwPhbw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcwPhbw.jpg&h=62dfe8d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為時間關係，最後我剩係夠時間上去瑪涅塔，因為佢除咗有展板睇之外，佢仲係全個城市嘅制高點，上面有觀景台可以飽覽成個Nimes嘅風景。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Sietij.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Sietij.jpg&h=7177adf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然睇落個景同之後見到嘅風景比可能冇乜特别，但係喺呢度深深感受到南法嗰種迷人嘅小鎮風情、好悠閑嘅渡假感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。最重要嘅係我喺法國嘅旅程要開始喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n待續。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:29:35.000Z","msg":"嗰競技場同神殿都幾靚<br />\n我學校離nimes唔洗一個鐘 但我無去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08bc8f0b3902cb849c967121edec9c4ecc66f3bc","tid":2179851,"uid":46808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:21:34.000Z","msg":"南法正呀 好想望住蔚藍海岸chill住過一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7358187cf9c5dddbb17ae416e4803ab80e9d208c","tid":2179851,"uid":277751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"好想去多次法國"},{"pid":"2763f677822130d519da1e63a589c3632745b858","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8580cbd60529d1ca93b0bdbb39e63708e422b0a3","tid":2179851,"uid":20160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb583f2e9285bad21607da937d2f34431fdf0e42","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f900dc1f44c807c2dd7a5326c3d4d9b2a5bea7c6","tid":2179851,"uid":20160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T12:21:58.000Z","msg":"Support, exchange 真係令人回味 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你果陣去邊呀？<br />\n<br />\n之前有機會去多一個sem<br />\n但係因為一啲原因去唔成<br />\n而家好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:57:06.000Z","msg":"我果時係澳洲<br />\n歐洲 exchange 班 fd 個個都去勻晒歐洲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:41:08.000Z","msg":"澳洲都唔錯呀，環島都可以玩好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947474779edac2419fdc892fb22d4147c240d63c","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"969f8de071b90ae06b6b8e10cf9545653c908acf","tid":2179851,"uid":312108,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e8b6ccc78e030a04923e78015249d281c7adf9d4","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T12:54:00.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"> <span class=\"large\">  【南法普羅旺斯尋覓芳草之旅】（二）Day 2（上）：古羅馬城市--尼姆市内半日遊   </span> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"> 是日路線：Nimes&rarr; Pont Du Gard<br />\n  </span><br />\n第二日起身喺附近搵咗間麵包鋪買咗兩個Croissant食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。唔知有冇人都覺得喺法國係冇難食嘅麵包，基本上求其搵一間麵包鋪、甚至就咁喺超市買都冇伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n作為窮鬼書生嘅我有唔少日子都係靠麵包渡日架。<br />\n<br />\n食完之後，我哋終於可以行下原本尋日要行嘅Nimes古城區。<br />\nNimes以前其實係一個古羅馬城填，因此景點係以古羅馬嘅遺跡為主。由於尋日冇咗一日嘅關係，我哋只係走馬看花咁去咗幾個主要景點打卡:<br />\n<br />\n尼姆競技場 Arena de Nimes<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cDVMjqj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcDVMjqj.jpg&h=769ab14f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n方形神殿 Maison Career<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pzj9hbQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPzj9hbQ.jpg&h=4a758ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瑪涅塔 la Tour Magne<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUHnCca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUHnCca.jpg&h=8cc8fc6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNimes景點嘅門票有好多唔同嘅組合，大家可以根據有嘅時間同想去嘅地方分開去買。<br />\n如果得半日，我諗最多都係好趕咁行到兩個，如果有一日就可以考慮買晒上述三個景點嘅門票。<br />\n門票詳情：<a href=\"https://www.arenes-nimes.com/en/prepare-your-visit/rates\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arenes-nimes.com%2Fen%2Fprepare-your-visit%2Frates&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zm0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=e4e78a2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.arenes-nimes.com/en/prepare-your-visit/rates</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QcwPhbw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQcwPhbw.jpg&h=62dfe8d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為時間關係，最後我剩係夠時間上去瑪涅塔，因為佢除咗有展板睇之外，佢仲係全個城市嘅制高點，上面有觀景台可以飽覽成個Nimes嘅風景。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Sietij.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Sietij.jpg&h=7177adf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然睇落個景同之後見到嘅風景比可能冇乜特别，但係喺呢度深深感受到南法嗰種迷人嘅小鎮風情、好悠閑嘅渡假感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。最重要嘅係我喺法國嘅旅程要開始喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n待續。。。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T14:29:35.000Z","msg":"嗰競技場同神殿都幾靚<br />\n我學校離nimes唔洗一個鐘 但我無去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:43:12.000Z","msg":"有時間見識下ok嘅，但係又未去到非去不可<br />\n多數連埋Pont Du Gard順便去打卡姐"},{"pid":"6a29cdfda01f4357eb8d21c35de2cabf3256d1d8","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08bc8f0b3902cb849c967121edec9c4ecc66f3bc","tid":2179851,"uid":46808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:21:34.000Z","msg":"南法正呀 好想望住蔚藍海岸chill住過一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"唉 我都想去再東南啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMarseille Nice真係度假勝地"},{"pid":"c58934d3ba518329ab06601a306fd5cc214abe09","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7358187cf9c5dddbb17ae416e4803ab80e9d208c","tid":2179851,"uid":277751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:22:32.000Z","msg":"好想去多次法國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:46:26.000Z","msg":"我都係！想去多好多好多次！<br />\n但係唔知幾時先有機會喇<br />\n而家法國武肺爆得好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63334aef231b613756b83a53a0f4ed93fdf85cbd","tid":2179851,"uid":312108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:37:02.000Z","msg":"樓主最近還好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876b7bcb67e454d8dcc7f652e6d68bae5a9b1d2a","tid":2179851,"uid":219244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a29cdfda01f4357eb8d21c35de2cabf3256d1d8","tid":2179851,"uid":372699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08bc8f0b3902cb849c967121edec9c4ecc66f3bc","tid":2179851,"uid":46808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T06:21:34.000Z","msg":"南法正呀 好想望住蔚藍海岸chill住過一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"唉 我都想去再東南啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nMarseille Nice真係度假勝地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T15:05:41.000Z","msg":"蔚藍海岸睇相真係好靚<br />\n地中海真係冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3158cfa24b232a3bf682000101ce2b29c85e7ef","tid":2179851,"uid":259716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"樓主還好嗎"},{"pid":"6772bfaadca24e4821ffc0f2043189f5f79972b6","tid":2179851,"uid":312108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3158cfa24b232a3bf682000101ce2b29c85e7ef","tid":2179851,"uid":259716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"樓主還好嗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"樓主快啲返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\"